[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    190[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** Minor rewrite of the HealthLake opening: "You need to pull together diagnoses, procedures, medications, labs, and encounter history for each patient at discharge time. HealthLake gives you a FHIR-native data store that normalizes clinical data from EHR systems into a queryable format. Its FHIR search capabilities make the feature assembly step cleaner than querying raw EHR databases directly." (Lead with the need, then introduce the service.)
